zh: 每隔固定时间获取一次API数据，例如航母存货和订单。请确保你在使用与你在右下角选择的一致的指挥官进行登录。你将需要每月重新认证。

column2: Percentage that a material name has to match. A lower value will increase false positives.

column2: Exact matching requires flawless recognition. Try fuzzy if you have issues detecting materials.
